lemma add_succ_zero (a : mynat) : a + succ(0) = succ(a) :=
lemma zero_add (n : mynat) : 0 + n = n :=
data.editorText:
induction n with d hd,
rw add_zero,

data.lean: lemma add_assoc (a b c : mynat) : (a + b) + c = a + (b + c) :=
data.editorText:
induction c with k hk,
-- base case
rw add_zero (a+b),
rw add_zero b,
refl,

--inductive step
rw add_succ (a+b) k,
rw add_succ b k,
rw add_succ a (b+k),
rw hk,
refl,

data.lean: lemma succ_add (a b : mynat) : succ a + b = succ (a + b) :=
data.editorText:
induction b with k hk,
--base case
rw add_zero (succ a),
rw add_zero a,
refl,

--inductive step
rw add_succ (succ a) k,
rw add_succ a k,
rw hk,
refl,

data.lean: lemma add_comm (a b : mynat) : a + b = b + a :=
data.editorText:
induction b with k hk,
-- base case
rw add_zero,
rw zero_add,
refl,

--inductive step
rw add_succ a k,
rw succ_add k a,
rw hk,
refl,

data.lean: theorem succ_eq_add_one (n : mynat) : succ n = n + 1 :=
data.editorText:
rw one_eq_succ_zero,
rw add_succ n 0,
rw add_zero n,
refl,

data.lean: lemma add_right_comm (a b c : mynat) : a + b + c = a + c + b :=
data.editorText:
rw add_assoc a b c,
rw add_comm b c,
rw ← add_assoc a c b,
refl,

data.lean: lemma zero_mul (m : mynat) : 0 * m = 0 :=
data.editorText:
induction m with k hk,
--base case
rw mul_zero 0,
refl,

--inductive step
rw mul_succ 0 k,
rw hk,
rw add_zero,
refl,

data.lean: lemma mul_one (m : mynat) : m * 1 = m :=
data.editorText:
rw one_eq_succ_zero,
rw mul_succ m 0,
rw mul_zero m,
rw zero_add m,
refl,

data.lean: lemma one_mul (m : mynat) : 1 * m = m :=
data.editorText:
induction m with k hk,
--base case
rw mul_zero 1,
refl,

--inductive step
rw mul_succ 1 k,
rw hk,
rw succ_eq_add_one k,
refl,

data.lean: lemma mul_add (t a b : mynat) : t * (a + b) = t * a + t * b :=
data.editorText:
induction b with k hk,
--base case
rw add_zero a,
rw mul_zero t,
rw add_zero (t*a),
refl,

--inductive pass
rw add_succ a k,
rw mul_succ t (a+k),
rw hk,
rw mul_succ t k,
rw add_assoc (t*a) (t*k) t,
refl,

data.lean: lemma mul_assoc (a b c : mynat) : (a * b) * c = a * (b * c) :=
data.editorText:
induction c with k hk,
--base case
rw mul_zero (a*b),
rw mul_zero b,
rw mul_zero a,
refl,

--inductive step
rw mul_succ,
rw hk,
rw ← mul_add a (b*k) b,
rw succ_eq_add_one k,
rw mul_add b k 1,
rw mul_one b,
refl,

data.lean: lemma succ_mul (a b : mynat) : succ a * b = a * b + b :=
data.editorText:
induction b with k hk,
--base case
rw mul_zero (succ a),
rw add_zero (a*0),
rw mul_zero a,
refl,

--inductive step
rw mul_succ (succ a) k,
rw add_succ ((succ a) * k) a,
rw hk,

rw add_succ (a * (succ k)) k,
rw succ_eq_add_one k,
rw mul_add a k 1,
rw mul_one a,
rw add_right_comm (a*k) a k,
refl,

data.lean: lemma add_mul (a b t : mynat) : (a + b) * t = a * t + b * t :=
data.editorText:
induction t with k hk,
--base case
rw mul_zero (a+b),
rw mul_zero a,
rw mul_zero b,
rw add_zero 0,
refl,

--inductive step
rw mul_succ (a+b) k,
rw hk,

rw succ_eq_add_one k,
rw mul_add a k 1,
rw mul_one a,
rw mul_add b k 1,
rw mul_one b,
rw add_right_comm (a*k) a (b*k + b),
rw ← add_assoc (a*k) (b*k) b,
rw add_assoc (a*k + b*k) b a,
rw add_comm b a,
refl,

data.lean: lemma mul_comm (a b : mynat) : a * b = b * a :=
data.editorText:
induction b with k hk,
--base case
rw mul_zero a,
rw zero_mul a,
refl,

--inductive step
rw mul_succ a k,
rw succ_mul k a,
rw hk,
refl,

data.lean: lemma mul_left_comm (a b c : mynat) : a * (b * c) = b * (a * c) :=
data.editorText:
rw ← mul_assoc a b c,
rw mul_comm a b,
rw mul_assoc b a c,
refl,

data.lean: lemma zero_pow_zero : (0 : mynat) ^ (0 : mynat) = 1 :=
lemma zero_pow_succ (m : mynat) : (0 : mynat) ^ (succ m) = 0 :=
data.editorText:
rw pow_succ 0 m,
rw mul_zero (0^m),
refl,

data.lean: lemma pow_one (a : mynat) : a ^ (1 : mynat) = a :=
data.editorText:
rw one_eq_succ_zero,
rw pow_succ a,
rw pow_zero a,
rw one_mul a,
refl,

data.lean: lemma one_pow (m : mynat) : (1 : mynat) ^ m = 1 :=
data.editorText:
induction m with k hk,
-- base case
rw pow_zero 1,
refl,

--inductive step
rw pow_succ 1,
rw hk,
rw mul_one 1,
refl,

data.lean: lemma pow_add (a m n : mynat) : a ^ (m + n) = a ^ m * a ^ n :=
data.editorText:
induction n with k hk,
--base case
rw add_zero m,
rw pow_zero a,
rw mul_one (a^m),
refl,

--inductive step
rw add_succ m k,
rw pow_succ a (m+k),
rw hk,
rw pow_succ a k,
rw mul_assoc (a^m) (a^k) a,
refl,

data.lean: lemma mul_pow (a b n : mynat) : (a * b) ^ n = a ^ n * b ^ n :=
data.editorText:
induction n with k hk,
--base case
rw pow_zero (a*b),
rw pow_zero a,
rw pow_zero b,
rw one_mul 1,
refl,

--inductive step
rw pow_succ (a*b) k,
rw hk,

rw pow_succ a k,
rw pow_succ b k,
rw mul_assoc (a^k) a ((b^k) * b),
rw mul_left_comm a (b^k) b,
rw ← mul_assoc (a^k) (b^k) (a*b),
refl,

data.lean: lemma pow_pow (a m n : mynat) : (a ^ m) ^ n = a ^ (m * n) :=
data.editorText:
induction n with k hk,
--base case
rw pow_zero (a^m),
rw mul_zero m,
rw pow_zero a,
refl,

--inductive step
rw pow_succ (a^m) k,
rw hk,
rw ← pow_add a (m*k) m,
rw ← mul_succ m k,
refl,

data.lean:
lemma add_squared (a b : mynat) :
  (a + b) ^ (2 : mynat) = a ^ (2 : mynat) + b ^ (2 : mynat) + 2 * a * b :=
data.editorText:
rw two_eq_succ_one,
rw succ_eq_add_one 1,
rw pow_add (a+b) 1 1,
rw pow_one (a+b),
rw mul_add (a+b) a b,
rw add_mul a b a,
rw add_mul a b b,
rw mul_comm b a,

rw pow_add a 1 1,
rw pow_one a,
rw pow_add b 1 1,
rw pow_one b,
rw mul_assoc (1 + 1) a b,
rw ← succ_eq_add_one 1,
rw succ_mul 1 (a*b),
rw one_mul (a*b),
rw add_assoc (a*a) (b*b) (a*b + a*b),
rw add_comm (b*b) (a*b + a*b),
rw add_assoc (a*b) (a*b) (b*b),
rw ← add_assoc (a*a) (a*b) (a*b + b*b),

refl,

data.lean: lemma and_or_distrib_left (P Q R : Prop) : P ∧ (Q ∨ R) ↔ (P ∧ Q) ∨ (P ∧ R) :=
data.editorText:
split,
--first part
  intro h,
  cases h with p qr,
  cases qr with q r,
  --case q
    left,
    split,
    --part p
      exact p,
    --part q
      exact q,
  --case r
    right,
    split,
    --part p
      exact p,
    --part r
      exact r,

--second part
intro h,
cases h with pq pr,
--case p^q
  cases pq with p q,
  split,
  --part p
    exact p,
  --part q or r
    left,
    exact q,
--case p^r
  cases pr with p r,
  split,
  --part p
    exact p,
  --part q or r
    right,
    exact r,

data.lean: lemma contrapositive2 (P Q : Prop) : (¬ Q → ¬ P) → (P → Q) :=
data.editorText:
intros h p',
repeat {rw not_iff_imp_false at h},
by_cases p : P; by_cases q : Q,
--case TT
exact q,
--case TF
have np := h q,
have boom := np p,
contradiction,
--case FT
exact q,
--case FF
rw not_iff_imp_false at p,
have boom := p p',
contradiction,
